		</div>
	</div>
</div></div></div><div class="vorteile wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-4 vc_col-has-fill"><div class="vc_column-inner vc_custom_1552236101758"><div class="wpb_wrapper">
	<div class="kleo_text_column wpb_text_column wpb_content_element " >
		<div class="wpb_wrapper">
			<h4>Services und Vorteile der Mitgliedschaft</h4>

		</div>
	</div><div class="wpb_single_image wpb_content_element vc_align_center"><figure class="wpb_wrapper vc_figure"><div class="vc_single_image-wrapper   vc_box_border_grey"><img class="vc_single_image-img " src="https://bvcp.de/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Mitgliedssiegel_rund_scharz-grau_150dpi-200x200.png" width="200" height="200" alt="Mitgliedssiegel_rund_scharz-grau_150dpi" title="Mitgliedssiegel_rund_scharz-grau_150dpi" /></div></figure></div>
	<div class="kleo_text_column wpb_text_column wpb_content_element " >
